            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="git-hooks-post-receive-shell">git hooks post-receive shell<a class="hash-link" href="#git-hooks-post-receive-shell" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h2><div class="language-shell codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#F8F8F2;--prism-background-color:#282A36"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-shell codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token shebang important">#!/bin/sh</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token assign-left variable" style="color:rgb(189, 147, 249);font-style:italic">git_folder</span><span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token plain">/usr/local/apache-tomcat-8.5.46-9487/webapps/repo</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token assign-left variable" style="color:rgb(189, 147, 249);font-style:italic">tomcat_folder</span><span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token plain">/usr/local/apache-tomcat-8.5.46-9487/webapps/ROOT</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token function" style="color:rgb(80, 250, 123)">rm</span><span class="token plain"> -rf </span><span class="token variable" style="color:rgb(189, 147, 249);font-style:italic">${git_folder}</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token function" style="color:rgb(80, 250, 123)">mkdir</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token variable" style="color:rgb(189, 147, 249);font-style:italic">${git_folder}</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token builtin class-name" style="color:rgb(189, 147, 249)">cd</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token variable" style="color:rgb(189, 147, 249);font-style:italic">${git_folder}</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token function" style="color:rgb(80, 250, 123)">git</span><span class="token plain"> --work-tree</span><span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token variable" style="color:rgb(189, 147, 249);font-style:italic">${git_folder}</span><span class="token plain"> --git-dir</span><span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token plain">/var/repo/qa.git checkout -f master</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token function" style="color:rgb(80, 250, 123)">rm</span><span class="token plain"> -rf src</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token function" style="color:rgb(80, 250, 123)">cp</span><span class="token plain"> -r </span><span class="token variable" style="color:rgb(189, 147, 249);font-style:italic">${git_folder}</span><span class="token plain">/dist/image/ </span><span class="token variable" style="color:rgb(189, 147, 249);font-style:italic">${tomcat_folder}</span><span class="token plain">/</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token function" style="color:rgb(80, 250, 123)">cp</span><span class="token plain"> -r </span><span class="token variable" style="color:rgb(189, 147, 249);font-style:italic">${git_folder}</span><span class="token plain">/dist/css/ </span><span class="token variable" style="color:rgb(189, 147, 249);font-style:italic">${tomcat_folder}</span><span class="token plain">/</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token function" style="color:rgb(80, 250, 123)">cp</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token variable" style="color:rgb(189, 147, 249);font-style:italic">${git_folder}</span><span class="token plain">/dist/js/main.js </span><span class="token variable" style="color:rgb(189, 147, 249);font-style:italic">${tomcat_folder}</span><span class="token plain">/js/</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg class="copyButtonIcon_y97N" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div><hr><h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="git-大小寫設定">Git 大小寫設定<a class="hash-link" href="#git-大小寫設定" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h2><p>關閉單一專案的大小寫忽略設定 (等同於開啟大小寫偵測)</p><div class="language-shell codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#F8F8F2;--prism-background-color:#282A36"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-shell codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain">$ </span><span class="token function" style="color:rgb(80, 250, 123)">git</span><span class="token plain"> config --local core.ignorecase </span><span class="token boolean">false</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg class="copyButtonIcon_y97N" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div><p>開啟單一專案的大小寫忽略設定 (等同於關閉大小寫偵測)</p><div class="language-shell codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#F8F8F2;--prism-background-color:#282A36"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-shell codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain">$ </span><span class="token function" style="color:rgb(80, 250, 123)">git</span><span class="token plain"> config --local core.ignorecase </span><span class="token boolean">true</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg class="copyButtonIcon_y97N" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
